;span class=&quot;comment html-comment&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- locale[NSW_EV001]/period[variable] --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment html-comment&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- non-warning-info-elements-exist=&#39;yes&#39; --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;folder&quot; id=&quot;folder7&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;forecast-period&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-name&quot;&gt;start-time-local&lt;/span&gt;=&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-value&quot;&gt;2025-11-26T03:00:00+11:00&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-name&quot;&gt;end-time-local&lt;/span&gt;=&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-value&quot;&gt;2025-11-27T00:00:00+11:00&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-name&quot;&gt;start-time-utc&lt;/span&gt;=&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-value&quot;&gt;2025-11-25T16:00:00Z&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-name&quot;&gt;end-time-utc&lt;/span&gt;=&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-value&quot;&gt;2025-11-26T13:00:00Z&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;opened&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 1em;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;text&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-name&quot;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;=&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-value&quot;&gt;information&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;For information on preparing for bushfires go to www.rfs.nsw.gov.au.&lt;span class=&quot;html-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/text&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;text&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-name&quot;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;=&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute-value&quot;&gt;synoptic_situation&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Hot to very hot and dry conditions will combine with fresh to strong and gusty west to northwest winds over much of New South Wales on Wednesday. Wind will begin to ease during the evening and shift west to southwesterly over western parts. Gusty thunderstorms are expected to develop over northern and eastern districts, most likely in the afternoon.&lt;span class=&quot;html-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/text&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/forecast-period&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment html-comment&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- =============== --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment html-comment&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- HAZARD ELEMENTS --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment html-comment&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- =============== --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment html-comment&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- locale[NSW_EV001]/period[day0] --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;folder&quot; id=&quot;folder8&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;html-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;forecast-period&lt;span class=&quot;html-attribute&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span clas